# webpy Applications

webpy applications encompasss the urls and handlers that map to them. They fall into several categories:

* [[/docs/0.3/apps/basic|Basic app]]. Define urls and classes to handle them.
* [[/docs/0.3/apps/auto|Auto app]]. Urls are determined automatically based on classes.
* [[/docs/0.3/apps/subdir|Subdir app]]. Run multiple apps on a single domain based on url.
* [[/docs/0.3/apps/subdomain|Subdomain app]]. Run multiple apps based on subdomains.